                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Uncertainty of +-4% in the Maximal Cross",
                "Section Originates from Counting Statistics (+-2.5%,",
                "MAINLY IN THE O-18 PEAK IN THE RUTHERFORD",
                "BACKSCATTERING SPECTROSCOPY SPECTRA OF THE SI/SI-O(2)-",
                "SAMPLES), Relative Beam Dose Measurements (+-1%), the",
                "Conversion of the Calibrated Cross Section (AT THE",
                "PLATEAU) To the Top (+-1.5%) And the Uncertainty in the",
                "Elastic  O-18(A,A)O-18  Scattering Cross Section at the",
                "Energy Below 2 MeV (+-3%).  It is Noted That at",
                "Energies Below 2 MeV, No Deviation from the (SCREENED)",
                "Rutherford Cross Section is Expected.  The Error of",
                "+-3% May Therefore be Too Pessimistic."
              ]
            }
          ],
